  "1768780": {
    "name": "剑与狐尾 (Of Blades & Tails)",
    "steam_appid": 1768780,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1768780/extras/0355e1b2d16c27fe9f295cc710338612.avif?t=1761316512\" width=616 height=96 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一款回合制角色扮演游戏，注重操作，但同时鼓励深思熟虑。 探索一片栖息着不同动物部落的奇妙土地。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在游戏中，你将扮演狐狸部落的聪明一员——瑞克。 不祥之兆接踵而至，维护动物王国和平的重任降到了你身上。 离开家乡，探索世界，你才能变得足够强大，制裁邪恶。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1768780/extras/77efaec60f8e3862dcaea62d342be07a.poster.avif?t=1761316512\" width=616 height=228 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1768780/extras/77efaec60f8e3862dcaea62d342be07a.webm?t=1761316512\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1768780/extras/77efaec60f8e3862dcaea62d342be07a.mp4?t=1761316512\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏灵感来自经典的刷宝游戏（如<i>《暗黑破坏神》</i>和回合制RPG（如<i>《马基埃亚尔的传说》</i>或<i>《紫色晶石》</i>）。 不过本游戏没有<strong>永久死亡</strong>。 这是一款<strong>易于上手且具有娱乐性</strong>的动作角色扮演游戏。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >故事剧情灵感来自经典的点击冒险游戏<i>《继承大地》</i>。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在你探索这片大地时，你将获得经验并解锁新能力。 并非所有居民都对你友好。 有些动物会为你提供信息，有些只对交易感兴趣，还有一些只会妨碍您。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1768780/extras/929d8f1c14c5dec08e2b653f998bd797.poster.avif?t=1761316512\" width=616 height=228 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1768780/extras/929d8f1c14c5dec08e2b653f998bd797.webm?t=1761316512\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1768780/extras/929d8f1c14c5dec08e2b653f998bd797.mp4?t=1761316512\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >改良装备并收集环境中有用的资源，以在战斗中取得决定性的优势。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1768780/extras/da50a4eeb53316f9ccc7ab27c4507b56.avif?t=1761316512\" width=616 height=96 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <strong>回合制战斗</strong>，快速行动和战略规划兼得</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 值得探索的<strong>开放世界</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <strong>新鲜自然、充满动物气息的环境</strong>，通过鲜活的像素美术呈现</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <strong>多种游戏模式</strong>，轻松游玩或是挑战自我，任尔选择</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <strong>程序生成</strong>的地牢和洞穴</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <strong>主线剧情</strong>和各种支线任务</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <strong>角色成长</strong>不分职业，多种能力可供解锁</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 不同品质的<strong>装备</strong>和有特殊属性的<strong>独特物品</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <strong>狩猎巨虫或收集草药</strong>以及其他有用资源</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <strong>敌人类型繁多</strong>，技能各异，需要战术决策</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <strong>加入派系</strong>，获得更高级的技能和装备</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 拼凑<strong>藏宝图</strong>，根据提示找到强大的护符</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <strong>与各个定居点的商人交易</strong>，出售珍贵的战利品</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 参与<strong>竞技场挑战</strong>，与其他玩家争夺高分</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1768780/extras/eec5ac594baf32b2bae273582017907f.poster.avif?t=1761316512\" width=616 height=340 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1768780/extras/eec5ac594baf32b2bae273582017907f.webm?t=1761316512\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1768780/extras/eec5ac594baf32b2bae273582017907f.mp4?t=1761316512\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
